             was indicted for <rs id="t18240407-104-off586" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18240407-104-off586" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240407-104-off586" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18240407-104-cd587" type="crimeDate">16th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240407-104-off586 t18240407-104-cd587"></join>, two bushels of chaff
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18240407-104-victim1006" type="victimName">
                  Henry 
                  Walker
               <interp inst="t18240407-104-victim1006" type="surname" value="Walker"></interp>
